HEADWORD: Rubric
<hw>Ru"bric</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To adorn ith red; to redden; to
rubricate.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

